      <hedline>
        <hl1>Environmental Paradox</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Sheldon B Cohen letter on Sept 26 article on debate over new pows</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>''Debate on Need for New Power Plants Ignores Conservation'' (news article, Sept. 26) describes the unlevel playing field in the world of energy today. We wail about greenhouse gases and pollution, yet our system is designed for waste, inefficiency and degradation of the environment.</p>
        <p>SHELDON B. COHEN  Atlanta, Sept. 28, 2000</p>
      </block>
